<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-secondary/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex justify-center w-full md:w-auto">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-muted flex items-center justify-center text-5xl font-bold text-muted-foreground select-none">
          GH
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-muted-foreground space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          My name is Guus, and I like to read. Uncertain on what to read, I went on holiday with my e-reader. During my holiday, I’d find books online which I’d want to read but was unable to load these onto my e-reader without a laptop at hand. 
        </p>
        <p>
          Out of that hassle came KoSync: a simple tool that allows me to synchronise books to my favourite KOBO e-reader and instantly start reading them.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ultimately, I want to remove the threshold people feel to start reading the books they like. KoSync allows people to find a book, upload it and start reading.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
